[@button]{FAST}The great hall of the Justice Buddies HQ, usually bustling with adventurers, robots, and aliens alike, now lays dormant. "Where have the Heroes gone?" cry the hapless citizens. To which no one answers.

For an unknown evil has struck the team. The {EMERGE}[RED]DANGEROUS ROOM{CLEARCOLOR}{ENDEMERGE}, the JB's holographic training simulator and Artificial Intelligence, has  run amok! Trapped in a hell of their own making, the Justice Buddies now must fight for their lives and find a way out.

Before the AI shut off communications, a single message was transmitted: "SEND HELP"

But who will answer the call?